Recoil
It is a powerful state management library
after installing recoil wrap the entire application within RecoilRoot
Create a new folder called atoms as we create slices while using redux
 - Atoms represent a piece of state which works excatly as useState except for useState is used
 works for a single component
 - then we use useRecoilState("key") to access the state